window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Calin has a bright future as the top Alchemy student in the entire Academy, and the clans are lining up to woo him. But when tragedy hits his family, Calin must make a choice. Stay at the academy and continue his rise as a powerful cultivator or leave and risk everything to help his little sister. This exciting Western Cultivation fantasy has progression, monsters, and no harem.</p>"; 
